text: Anaxagorea phaeocarpa is a species of plant in the Annonaceae family. It is found in Costa Rica and Honduras. ==References== * Nelson, C. 1998. Anaxagorea phaeocarpa. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 20 August 2007.
